'''Stewart Copeland''' is a musician who wrote and performed the opening theme song&mdash;"[[In Trouble Again]]"&mdash;for the [[Star Wars: Droids: The Adventures of R2-D2 and C-3PO|''Star Wars Droids'']] animated television series. Copeland is famous for being the drummer of the band [[Wikipedia:The Police|The Police]].

